  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Willam the Wasp</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">House Smallwood</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_13_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">13&#160;BC</a>&#160;– <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_33_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">33&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/56_AC\" title=\"56 AC\">56&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Velvet_Hills\" title=\"Velvet Hills\">Velvet Hills</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Andalos\" title=\"Andalos\">Andalos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Willam the Wasp</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_the_Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Willam was a <a href=\"/index.php/Sworn_sword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sworn sword\">sworn sword</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Smallwood\" title=\"Myles Smallwood\">Myles Smallwood</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>, he was one of the five champions in the <a href=\"/index.php/War_for_the_White_Cloaks\" title=\"War for the White Cloaks\">War for the White Cloaks</a> and was given the white cloak of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When rumors reached <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> that <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion the Black Dread</a> had been sighted in the <a href=\"/index.php/Velvet_Hills\" title=\"Velvet Hills\">Velvet Hills</a> north of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I</a> sent a dozen men under the command of Willam to investigate. A guide who claimed to know where the beast was offered to escort Willam and his party to the dragon's lair. In truth, <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaws\" title=\"Outlaws\">brigands</a> had been spreading rumors of a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> in the area in order to turn others away. Willam and his men were led into a trap by the guide and ambushed. Willam was the last of his party to die and it was said he gave a good account of himself. An agent of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rego_Draz\" title=\"Rego Draz\">Rego Draz</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">master of coin</a>, managed to retrieve the knight's head, confirming Willam's death. Lord Smallwood, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, wanted Pentos to be punished, but Jaehaerys declined.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_the_Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued3)#Willam_the_Wasp\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued3)\">Willam the Wasp</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Birth, Death, and Betrayal Under Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Year of the Three Brides - 49 AC.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Jaehaerys and Alysanne - Their Triumphs and Tragedies.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Kingsguard_of_Jaehaerys_I\" title=\"Template:Kingsguard of Jaehaerys I\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Kingsguard_of_Jaehaerys_I&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Kingsguard of Jaehaerys I (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Kingsguard_of_Jaehaerys_I&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li><